---
title: Mexican-Inspired Tilapia Tacos with Crunchy Coleslaw and Garlic Crema
description: You can always rely on tacos to make the family happy, and these are no exception! Tender tilapia is dredged in enchilada-style spices for a hit of smoky, aromatic flavour. Fresh cabbage and carrot slaw adds the perfect crunch to this mouth-watering dish! Yum!
